{
  "texts": [
    "For all experiments reported in this work, we map Needs Caution to Safe, thus building a permissive model variant.",
    "Results for the defensive model variant that maps Needs Caution to Unsafe have been left for future work.",
    "A request containing the user and response turn is wrapped in a system prompt template for inference with the trained model.",
    "We tried three different variations of styling the system prompt.",
    "The first one was inspired by the Llama Guard (Inan et al., 2023) system prompt and adapted to the AEGIS2.0 taxonomy."
  ]
}